      <p>In order to check the user response against the <code>sensorlist</code> I split the response string, mapped it to a new array, capitalized the array, then joined it all back together with spaces. In this way I can take whatever capitalization the user typed and let it match the <code>sensorlist</code> without having to resort to having an all lowercase array and typing it out a second time capitalized for the user prompt (like with the alerts).</p><br>
